{
  "text": "is a monotonically increasing sequence in t, for any given systems {Q m } n m=1 . Similar results to Lemma III-A.1 and III-A.2 appear in [CITATION_1] , and hence the proof details are omitted here. Given the fact in Lemma III-A.2, the lower and upper bound sequences can be simplified to",
